QuestData.Title: Walk Among Death
QuestData.Description:
This trench echoes with necromantic energies unleashed in the countless battles waged here. That power has coalesced into chaotic entities we call deathwalkers.
In simpler times, we would have sent troops out to subdue them to serve the House of the Chosen. But with war brewing, there is no time for that.
Eliminate this potential threat, before our enemies turn them against us.
QuestData.RewardText: Everything in this land is dangerous. There is no room for weakness.
